## 🚀 Overview
This repository contains the source code for my professional portfolio. It is engineered to showcase my expertise in **Gameplay Programming, Systems Architecture, and Game Development**. The interface is designed with a tactile, retro-inspired aesthetic that reflects my passion for immersive digital experiences.

## 🛠️ Technical Stack
Built with a focus on performance, modularity, and modern web standards:

<div align="center">
  <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/react-%2320232a.svg?style=for-the-badge&logo=react&logoColor=%2361DAFB" alt="React" />
  <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/typescript-%23007ACC.svg?style=for-the-badge&logo=typescript&logoColor=white" alt="TypeScript" />
  <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/vite-%23646CFF.svg?style=for-the-badge&logo=vite&logoColor=white" alt="Vite" />
  <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/tailwindcss-%2338B2AC.svg?style=for-the-badge&logo=tailwind-css&logoColor=white" alt="TailwindCSS" />
  <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Framer_Motion-black?style=for-the-badge&logo=framer&logoColor=blue" alt="Framer Motion" />
</div>

<br>

- **Core:** React 18 + TypeScript
- **Build Tool:** Vite (for rapid HMR and optimized bundling)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS (utility-first, responsive design)
- **Animations:** Framer Motion (fluid, hardware-accelerated transitions)
- **Icons:** Lucide React & React Icons
- **Deployment:** Replit / Vercel CI

## 🎯 Architecture & Features
- **Dynamic Project Showcase:** Interactive, scalable modal system displaying detailed intel, technical features, and gameplay footage for projects like *House of Lies*, *Prisma*, and *Recording 2:17*.
- **Clean Component Structure:** Highly modular architecture ensuring the codebase remains organized and easily maintainable.
- **Performance Optimized:** Lazy loading of high-resolution assets and optimized dependency management.
- **Responsive UI/UX:** Fully adaptable interface that maintains fidelity across desktop, tablet, and mobile displays.

